title: Bryant McFadden on five teams to make playoffs in 2018 (Football 07/11)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Bryant McFadden to break down five teams who will jump up and make the playoffs in 2018, including two choices that might be obvious: the Chargers and the Packers. The guys also break down some sleeper options (Bears?? Giants??) who could make the leap into the postseason after missing out last year.
